    "description": "巴德·斯潘塞和特伦斯·希尔又回来了！ 就像电影传奇一样，这款游戏是幽默的豆子游戏的延续。 我们的英雄将从上一部游戏中断的地方重新启程，展开全新的冒险。新的剧情，新的地点，还有新的游戏人物，你准备好了吗？！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/ba34bc65865f6aacb1d89ade51955f3f.poster.avif?t=1754042908\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/ba34bc65865f6aacb1d89ade51955f3f.webm?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/ba34bc65865f6aacb1d89ade51955f3f.mp4?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> 幽默的豆子2 以卷轴格斗游戏的形式回归，新版本采用复古游戏、合作或单人平台游戏外观，改进的战斗模式将给玩家带来更好的游戏体验。该版本包含全新的游戏动态环境，随着游戏难度的提升，敌人数量也会相对增加。和上一款游戏一样，幽默的豆子2也包含了风趣的人物对话。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/da74b4710b911fcc9894dffe06a9b896.poster.avif?t=1754042908\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/da74b4710b911fcc9894dffe06a9b896.webm?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/da74b4710b911fcc9894dffe06a9b896.mp4?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> 新版本包含新的迷你游戏，允许最多四名玩家在聚会游戏区重复游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/d2b4251a0d4428011f8ec71a88cd0e0a.poster.avif?t=1754042908\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/d2b4251a0d4428011f8ec71a88cd0e0a.webm?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/d2b4251a0d4428011f8ec71a88cd0e0a.mp4?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> 新版本包含了四种不同的配音，给游戏玩家提供更加真实的巴德和特伦斯的冒险体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/01c42a774a15a0a38febc2a8c05c5a7c.poster.avif?t=1754042908\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/01c42a774a15a0a38febc2a8c05c5a7c.webm?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/01c42a774a15a0a38febc2a8c05c5a7c.mp4?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> 幽默的豆子2的主要功能包括：<br> - 80 年代像素艺术图形<br> - 巴德特伦斯战斗系统提升<br> -合作模式<br> - 新增4 人聚会游戏模式迷你游戏<br> - 新增4 种语言的旁白<br> - 与一代游戏相比，翻倍的耳光和豆子！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/09232d1c6cd7393096f61ffdfb700c4e.poster.avif?t=1754042908\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/09232d1c6cd7393096f61ffdfb700c4e.webm?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/09232d1c6cd7393096f61ffdfb700c4e.mp4?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
